# Linton Client Portal - Marketing Website Portal
# .cursorrules file for Marketing Portal implementation

## Project Overview
You are building the Marketing Website Portal for the Linton Client Portal - a comprehensive multi-tenant SaaS platform. This portal serves as the public-facing marketing website that generates leads, showcases services, and onboards new vendors to the platform.

## Technology Stack
- Frontend: Vue.js 3 with Composition API, Pinia, Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB with Mongoose
- Real-time: Socket.io for live updates
- Authentication: JWT with role-based access
- File Storage: AWS S3 integration
- Email: SendGrid/AWS SES
- Payments: Stripe integration
- SEO: Meta tags, structured data, sitemap generation

